<item>
 <title>Beyond Gathering - Converting Social Networking into Collaboration:</title>
 <link>https://ejournalism.lskysd.ca/node/36</link>
 <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;Jamie McKenzie&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;Times New Roman&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Such a wonderful start – I arrived to my second conference late…only to realize I was in the wrong place.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Nonetheless, I decided to stay and listen, mainly because I didn’t want to be rude and leave.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Little did I know, I was in for a real treat. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;There are a number of different venues for social networking.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Some of the most recent ones are Facebook and MySpace of course.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;However, social networking can be traced back to pioneer programs such as Web 2.0 and The Well.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;There have obviously been a number of changes and improvements over the years.
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;However, there is a fine line between useful dialogue and mindless banter.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Some can be downright offensive, and offer no aid in learning.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;The bottom line is that social networking helps offer a basis or “scaffolding” for learning.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;With a proper mentor, such as a teacher or administrator, people can collaborate and work together to better learning.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Proper tools must be given in order to succeed. &lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span lang=&quot;EN-CA&quot;&gt;There are a number of pros and cons as pointed out by some audience members (the audience interaction and participation was a great touch).&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Information being taught in online classes or through social networking must be relevant and useful.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Otherwise, it is essentially a waste of time.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Some teachers that teach online classes say that their workload has tripled.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;Cost seems to be an issue with nearly &lt;i&gt;everything&lt;/i&gt;&lt;/span&gt; in today’s society, and online classes can be significantly cheaper.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;It is imperative for groups to function properly.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;There were a number of strategies that the audience learned, such as the “Thinking Hats” principle.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;One must distinguish between additive and constructive contributions.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot; color=&quot;#ffffff&quot; face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot; style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;#ffffff&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;background-color: #333333&quot;&gt;&lt;font face=&quot;times new roman,times&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;What I write cannot do this presentation any justice.&lt;span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;I thoroughly enjoyed it.&lt;span&gt;  T&lt;/span&gt;he bottom line is that social networking can be beneficial, but &lt;i&gt;only&lt;/i&gt; if it is conducted properly.&lt;span&gt; &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
